                  <div className="mx-auto text-5xl w-max leading-snug place-items-stretch">
                    <span className="italic font-serif">you</span> CAN BREAK{" "}
                    <br></br> THESE CATEGORIES,<br></br> ALSO KNOWN AS GENRES
